com.ardic.android.iotignite.interfaces

Interface IThingManager

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    ThingManager

    public interface IThingManager
    Manager class for Thing objects. Every node implicitly has one ThingManager instance. With an instance you can manage your Thing's easily. Simply you can get instance by calling; myNode -> your Node object. ThingManager myThingManager = myNode.getThingManager();
    Author:
    ARDIC

    • Method Detail

      • registerThing

        boolean registerThing(Thing thing)
        Register Thing to assigned Node. NOTE : You CANNOT add any Thing objects to "Built-in Sensors, Built-in Processors" nodes. These Nodes are reserved and using by device itself.
        Parameters:
        thing - : Thing object which to be registered.
        Returns:
        true | false : Registration status of Thing.

      • unregisterThing

        Parameters:
        thingID: - ThingID string which to be unregistered.
        boolean - : Unregistration status of Thing.

      • getEveryThing

        List<Thing> getEveryThing()
        Get all Thing's managed by this manager. Returns Thing's list assigned to manager.
        Returns:
        thingList : Returns list of Thing's if no object(s) as assigned that name returns empty list.

      • getThingByName

        List<Thing> getThingByName(String thingName)
        Get Thing object(s) with specified name. List of Thing's. List could be have zero to many elements. Because Thing name is NOT UNIQUE.
        Parameters:
        thingName - : Name of Thing(s).
        Returns:
        thingList : Returns Thing object . If no object(s) as assigned that name returns empty list.

      • getThingByID

        Thing getThingByID(String thingID)
        Get Thing object from ID. Thing ID is UNIQUE.
        Parameters:
        thingID - : ID of Thing.
        Returns:
        thingObject: Returns Thing object of assigned id. If no object as assigned that id returns null object.

      • sendData

        boolean sendData(Thing thing)

        Parameters:
